&lt;p&gt;[[Broomhead I]]: 26 has transliteration and notes containing the following translations: &lt;br&gt;
a3 ten traus of oil of sesame with milk &lt;br&gt;
a4 makes [it] very white. &lt;br&gt;
b1 [is to be applied] as an embrocation in milk on the stomach. &lt;br&gt;
b3 butter [and] oil of sesame with milk &lt;br&gt;
b5 [and] oil of sesame is to be cooked in milk.&lt;/p&gt; </item>
